title: 3. Know Yourself, Know Your Worth
itunes:title: Know Yourself, Know Your Worth
description:
Hey ya'll!

 In this episode, we get into knowing your worth, understanding where your worth DOESN'T come from, and finally understanding where your worth DOES comes from.  Sit back, relax, and enjoy this week's episode ya'll.

 

Don't forget to please rate, review & subscribe!
